Package net.bubbaland.trivia.client.tabpanel

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnswerEntryPanel
    Creates a dialog box that prompts user to propose an answer.
    AnswerQueuePanel
    A panel that shows the submitted answers for the current round.
    CumulativePointsChartPanel
    A panel with a stacked XY plot that shows the cumulative score by round.
    HistoryPanel
    A panel to select and display any round.
    OpenQuestionsPanel
    A panel which displays a list of the current open questions.
    PlaceChartPanel
    A panel with a chart showing announced place by round.
    RoundPanel
    A panel for the current round data.
    RoundQuestionsPanel
    A panel that shows all of the questions for a round.
    ScoreByRoundChartPanel
    A panel that displays a stacked bar chart showing the score in each round.
    ScoreByRoundPanel
    A panel that displays the scores from each round.
    StandingsPanel  
    SummaryPanel
    A panel which displays summary information of the trivia contest.
    TeamComparisonPanel
    A panel with a chart comparing all of the teams' scores.
    WorkflowPanel
    A panel for the workflow tab, which contains most of the trivia operations
